content:
The Insurance Policy 360° Console enables service agents to manage interactions and streamline common tasks. For example, Identity Verification allows agents to search accounts, verify customers, and improve the customer experience.

A Profile Card displays basic account information, an Engagement Timeline provides a record of previous activity, and Record Alerts display relevant notifications in context. Policies are also displayed, allowing easy access to all actions available in context.

Identity Verification verifies customers and enhances the customer experience. Record Alerts alert agents to changes in client records that require action.
title: Insurance Policy Management with 360° Console
